title: Introducing Mayim Bialik's Breakdown
description: Armed with a Phd in Neuroscience and plenty of personal experience, Mayim Bialik connects with special guests and breaks down the things that make us break down. Episodes include insightful interviews, personal stories, practical advice, and signs to watch out for.  See www.bialikbreakdown.com to 'Ask Mayim Anything' and have a chance to get your question answered on air.
author: askmayim@bialikbreakdown.com (Mayim Bialik)
